data.description: Charming 3-bed, 2-bath home featuring an isolated primary bedroom with a stylish barn door,  separating the bedroom from the vanity,   walk in closet and walk-in shower. The entire home boasts a consistent and modern touch with re finished epoxy countertops, ensuring durability and style. Two bedrooms share a guest bath, and one includes a cozy window seat. The kitchen features a dining area, and the easy-to-landscape yard is complemented by a 10x16 shop complete with electricity. Complete with newly installed solar panels for a consistent energy rate.  Solar panels must be assumed, so take advantage! Why take a chance on high energy bills during the freezing months or sweltering summers when you could enjoy a constant monthly energy rate of $140!  You are going to be paying the energy bill regardless of the amount, so why not buy knowing exactly what you will be paying every single month. No surprises!!
